@node "Install&Start" "4.  Installing and starting"
After you have unpacked FunTris-archive, game is ready to use.

If you want make sure, that FunTris will find all required files, you can
add this line to your "@{b}Sys:S/User-StartUp@{ub}"-file: "@{b}Assign FunTris:
DH1:Games/FunTris/@{ub}" (or whatever your FunTris-directory is).

After that you are ready to start playing. Just double-click FunTris-icon.
@endnode

@node "Instructions" "5.  Short instructions"
Usually no-one is interested to read any kind of documents, so let's make
this really short:

There is online-help (bottom of screen) on main menu- and player selection-
screens, so it would be really easy to start playing this game.

Also, I think that everyone know how to play tetris, so there's no need to
